{
  "stem": "11175.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We came to that barrack, more than 500 people, more than 500 people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody-- first of all, there was nowhere to-- assigned a place where you should be, sleep, or move.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was empty boards, completely empty boards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And excuse me, the cockroaches was running around in front of you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to lay down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No covers to cover themself, nothing behind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, I'm talking about mattresses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When we-- we got that food, the soup, what they're supposed to be for this people, which they would come back from work, from [NON-ENGLISH], so we had that soup.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When they started, they said, [INAUDIBLE]-- you know, for a day, for almost two days not to eat, everybody was pushing themselves to get that little soup.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we had the little soup.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we ate up the soup, and we went to lay down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a kapo there, an assigned kapo from before, from this group, the kapo remained there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they start to chase us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, I-- it's like even dogs you cannot chase like that, but they-- they-- they-- [MAKES NOISE] knocking over the head, and over the feet, and over the body.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Go!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Fast.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Fast.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Fast!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "More fast.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lay down, and don't stay in their-- under the way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was evening already, because we came in, this was late afternoon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they're supposed to come back from work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they came back from work, and they made the selection there also.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the rest, we were-- so we laid down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the morning, we got up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This appell outside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They put us together, and they start to-- to divide it-- the groups-- this group here, and this group here, this group-- and I was assigned to the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
